scope: >
  JVM java.sql.Driver shim for the scljet SQLite engine.
  New module runtime/std/scljet-jdbc-plugin/ (java.sql.* interfaces delegating
  to the pure scljet/jdbc.ssc facade via an embedded Interpreter). build.sbt
  wiring only. Does NOT touch scljet/*.ssc (owned by scljet-m3-writes /
  scljet-typed-decode), SPRINT.md, or sibling claims.
